I"i<h1 id="openproject-411">OpenProject 4.1.1</h1>

<p>OpenProject 4.1.1 has been released which includes a bug fix for the
roadmap and a design fix.</p>

<p>Due to a wrong link, an internal error was displayed in OpenProject
4.1.0 when trying to edit a version from the roadmap screen. This has
been fixed with OpenProject 4.1.1
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/20094">#20094</a>).</p>

<p>Additionally, the width for the column selection screen on the work
package page has been increased
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/20095">#20095</a>).</p>

<p>For further information on the release, please refer to the <a href="https://community.openproject.org/versions/714" title="Changelog v.4.0.10">Changelog
v.4.1.1</a>Â or
take a look at
<a href="https://github.com/opf/openproject/tree/v4.1.1" title="GitHub">GitHub</a>.</p>

